00:02:22,467 --> 00:02:26,249
What that means is that people who work for Big Viking Games

49
00:02:26,249 --> 00:02:28,250
should be very big fans of the work that we're doing.

50
00:02:28,250 --> 00:02:29,750
And the players that play our games

51
